@NODE MAIN "TABLE OF CONTENTS"

              How to Create Realistic Synthetic Sounds in MED

                                    by

                               Fergus Duniho

        @{" Preface " LINK 0.}

    BASIC HARMONIC SYNTHESIS TECHNIQUES

        @{" Introduction " LINK 1.}
        @{" Creating Harmonics " LINK 2.}
        @{" Mixing Harmonics " LINK 3.}

